# Cursor Rules for ARTi Platform

> **Note**: This legacy file is kept for backward compatibility. All rules have been migrated to `.cursor/rules/*.mdc` files which are more reliable for cloud agents and agent mode. See the rules directory for the authoritative versions.

## Quick Start

**Before starting ANY task, read:**
1. `docs/AGENT-QUICK-START.md` - Essential reference
2. `docs/BRANCHING-STRATEGY.md` - Navigation guide
3. `docs/AGENTIC-INFRASTRUCTURE.md` - Issue pipeline guide

**Branch naming**: `{type}/{app}/{description}` (e.g., `feature/spotify/playlist-filter`)

## Rules Index

All detailed rules live in `.cursor/rules/`:

| Rule File | Purpose | Activation |
|-----------|---------|------------|
| `platform-context.mdc` | Platform structure, apps, tech stack, cross-app patterns | Agent-decided |
| `spotify-patterns.mdc` | Spotify DB schema, code patterns, pitfalls | Agent-decided + glob |
| `youtube-patterns.mdc` | YouTube routing, auth, patterns | Agent-decided + glob |
| `soundcloud-patterns.mdc` | SoundCloud patterns, member portal, credits | Agent-decided + glob |
| `agentic-issue-protocol.mdc` | Creating GitHub issues for bugs/features | Agent-decided |
| `platform-support-agent.mdc` | Answering platform questions from knowledge base | Agent-decided |

